Key Match Events: Rangers left fielder Travis Jankowski skied high above the wall to take a walk-off homer away from Andrew Vaughn in the ninth inning of a 4-3 loss
Miscellaneous Highlights: The White Sox lost 3-1 to the Rangers before the sparsest of crowds in the first of two games Wednesday at Guaranteed Rate Field.
The Sox lost 4-3 to the Rangers in the nightcap, with a couple of hundred fans in attendance.
Others: The White Sox have now lost 103 games this season.
